    "The non zeros entries of U •p can be directly calculated knowing the covariance parameters and the number of neighbors M by following the algorithm available in (Katzfuss et al., 2020).",
    "And so a conditional draw is simply:",
    "Here w o is not sampled.",
    "Prediction at unsampled locations is carried out in two steps: in the first step, we predict the response at censored locations using the non-censored observations and adjust these predictions with the Mills ratio (Heckman, 1979).",
